<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She revealed she's expecting her first child with boyfriend Matt Sarsfield last month. </p>

<p>And pregnant Charlotte Dawson appeared in great spirits as she treated herself to McDonald's at one of the fast food restaurant's Manchester branches earlier this week. </p>

<p>The Ex On The Beach star, 27, enjoyed a relaxing ride around the English city in Missguided's Rolls Royce, where insiders claimed she was in final discussions for her very own maternity collection with the brand. </p>

<p>Oh baby! Pregnant Charlotte Dawson appeared in great spirits as she treated herself to McDonald's at one of the fast food restaurant's Manchester branches earlier this week</p>

<p>Cradling her growing baby bump, the mother-to-be opted for comfort in a blue jumper dress, which she paired with cycling shorts and perspex heels. </p>

<p>Switching into a second outfit, the Celebs Go Dating star looked radiant in an animal print dress, which was toned down with nude peep-toe stilettos. </p>

<p>The daughter of late comedian Les Dawson upped the style ante by accessorising her look with a elegant watch and circular-framed shades.</p>

<p>While her tresses were won in bouncy curls, Charlotte accentuated her beauty with dewy foundation, fluttery false lashes and pale pink lipgloss. </p>

